---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Hayub Idowu" description="About Hayub Idowu, developer and writer.">
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Hi, I'm Hayub Idowu — a developer writing about web technologies,
      design systems, and whatever I'm building at the moment.
    </p>

    <h2>This Site</h2>
    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a> and
      <a href="https://tailwindcss.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tailwind CSS</a>.
      Blog posts are authored in Markdown using Astro Content Collections.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site ships three switchable visual themes — Minimal, Bold, and Terminal —
      all implemented as CSS custom property sets. Switch between them using the
      dropdown in the header.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/HayubIdowu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
